user Must Click The Confirm Button one
user Must Click The Attachment Option
user Must Click The Upload File Button
user Must Redirect to Patient details Screen one
user Must Click On End Visit Option
user Must Click The Start Visit Option two
user Must Click The Confirm Button two
user Must Click The Capture Vitalas Option
user Must Enter The Height in Height Field
user Must Click The next Button three
user Must Enter The Weight in Weight Field
user Must Click The next Button Four
user Must Click The Save Form Option And Then Click Save Button
user Must Click The End Visit Option and Then click The Yes Button
user Must Redirect to Patient details Screen two
user Must Click The Merge Visit Option and Select The Merge List
user Must Click The Merge Selected Visit and Click The Return Page
user Must Click The Add Past Visit then Click The Cancel Button
user Must Click The Delete Patient Option
user Must Give The Reason And Then Click Confirm Button
user Must Pass the Patient Id In Find Patient Record Search box
